# Live Job Details Status for Today in Eastern Time zone
### This report shows a live snapshot of todays ETL job statuses in descending order
*Note - *visuals are refreshed continuously and support drill through*

## Successes ##
*Note - *Drillthrough is available to PipelineRundID for specifics, please right click a PipelineRundID and drill through as needed.*

## Failures ##
*Note - *Drillthrough is available to PipelineRundID for specifics, please right click a PipelineRundID and drill through as needed.*

# Job Execution Activity Overview
### This report shows all activtiy details for the selected Job execution
*Note - *the specifics come from the Job_Details_Overview page, please drill through from a PipelineRunID to properly utilize this page.  Additionally, Drill through by ActivityRunID for further investigation*

# Live High Level overview of Job and actvity details
### This page provided a high level summary of current Job and activity process statuses for the current day.
*Note - *This page does not support drill through*
## Total Insert Count For Current Day ##

# Activity Execution Overview
### This report shows all activtiy details for the selected activity
*Note - *the specifics come from the Job Execution Activity Overview page, please drill through a ActivityRunID to properly utilize this page.*

queries.text:
let Failed =    
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Failed"
    | project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, Failed_status = ItemRunStatus, Failed_time = EventDateTime;
let Succeeded =
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Succeeded"
    | project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, Success_status = ItemRunStatus, Success_time = EventDateTime;
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
    | join kind=leftouter (Succeeded) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | join kind=leftouter (Failed) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "In Progress" and Failed_status == '' and Success_status == '' and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | project  ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, PipelineRunID = ItemRunID, start_status = ItemRunStatus, start_time = ESTTime
    | order by start_time desc

let InProgress =
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
| extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
| project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, StartStatus = ItemRunStatus, Start_time = ESTTime;
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
| join kind=inner InProgress on ItemID and ItemRunID
| extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
| where ItemRunStatus  == "Succeeded" and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
| extend Duration_mins = datetime_diff('minute', ESTTime, Start_time)
| extend Last_Run_Duration = datetime_diff('minute', ESTTime - 1d, Start_time - 1d)
| project ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, PipelineRunID = ItemRunID, Start_time, Success_status = ItemRunStatus, Success_time = ESTTime, Duration_mins, Last_Run_Duration
| order by Start_time desc

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend  ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Failed" and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | count

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend  ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Succeeded" and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | count

Item_Data_Entity_Refined
| extend StartESTTime = DataEntityStartDateTime - 4h
| where StartESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
| project InsertCount
| summarize Total_Insert_Count = sum(InsertCount)

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend  ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Succeeded" and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | count

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend  ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Failed" and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | count

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
| join kind=leftouter (ItemDataEntity) on ItemRunID
| extend StartESTTime = DataEntityStartDateTime - 4h
| extend EndESTTime = DataEntityEndDateTime - 4h
| extend duration_mins = datetime_diff('minute', EndESTTime, StartESTTime)
| distinct PipeLineRunID = ItemRunID, ActivityName = DataEntityActivityName, Status = DataEntityExecutionStatus, ActivityRunID = DataEntityActivityRunID, StartTime = StartESTTime, EndTime = EndESTTime, Duration_Mins = duration_mins, EntityName = DataEntityName, InsertCount, RowsCopied
| where PipeLineRunID == PipelineRunID
| order by EndTime desc;

let InProgress =
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
| extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
| project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, StartStatus = ItemRunStatus, Start_time = ESTTime;
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
| join kind=inner InProgress on ItemID and ItemRunID
| extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
| where ItemRunStatus  == "Failed" and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
| extend Duration_mins = datetime_diff('minute', ESTTime, Start_time)
| extend Last_Run_Duration = datetime_diff('minute', ESTTime - 1d, Start_time - 1d)
| project ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, PipelineRunID = ItemRunID, Start_time, Failed_status = ItemRunStatus, Failed_time = ESTTime, Duration_mins, Last_Run_Duration
| order by Start_time desc

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
| project ItemName, ItemRunID
| where ItemRunID == PipelineRunID

Item_Data_Entity_Refined
| extend StartESTTime = DataEntityStartDateTime - 4h
| extend EndESTTime = DataEntityEndDateTime - 4h
| where StartESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York')) and ItemRunID == PipelineRunID
| project InsertCount
| summarize Total_Insert_Count = sum(InsertCount)

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
| project ItemWorkspaceName, ItemRunID
| where ItemRunID  == PipelineRunID

let Failed =    
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, Completed_status = ItemRunStatus, Completed_time = EventDateTime;
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
    | join kind=leftouter (Failed) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "In Progress" and Completed_status == '' and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | count

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend  ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | count

let End =    
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, PipelineRunID = ItemRunID, End_Time = ESTTime, End_Status = ItemRunStatus;
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
    | join kind=inner (End) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "In Progress" and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | extend Duration_Mins = datetime_diff('minute', End_Time, ESTTime)
    | extend Last_Run_Duration = datetime_diff('minute', End_Time - 1d, ESTTime - 1d)
    | project ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, PipelineRunID = ItemRunID, Start_Status = ItemRunStatus, start_time = ESTTime, End_Status, End_Time, Duration_Mins, Last_Run_Duration
    | order by Duration_Mins desc  
    | top 10 by Duration_Mins

Item_Data_Entity_Refined
| extend StartESTTime = DataEntityStartDateTime - 4h
| extend EndESTTime = DataEntityEndDateTime - 4h
| project ActivityName = DataEntityActivityName, DataEntityActivityRunID, EntityName = DataEntityName, StartESTTime, EndESTTime, InsertCount, RowsCopied, RowsRead
| where InsertCount != '' and EndESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
| order by InsertCount desc
| top 10 by InsertCount

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
| extend PipelineIdMessage = "Please drill through ActivityRunID on failed activity for more information"
| extend ErrorMessage = case(
    ExecutionErrorMessage == '', "No Errors Found", PipelineIdMessage
)
| project ErrorMessage, ExecutionErrorMessage, ItemRunID
| where ItemRunID == PipelineRunID

Item_Data_Entity_Refined
| project DataEntityActivityName, DataEntityActivityRunID
| where DataEntityActivityRunID == ActivityRunID

Item_Data_Entity_Refined
| extend StartESTTime = DataEntityStartDateTime - 4h
| extend TotalCount = iff(isnull(InsertCount) or InsertCount == 0, 0, InsertCount)
| where DataEntityActivityRunID == ActivityRunID
| project InsertCount = TotalCount

Item_Data_Entity_Refined
| project DataEntityWorkspaceName, DataEntityActivityRunID
| where DataEntityActivityRunID  == ActivityRunID

Item_Data_Entity_Refined
| extend ErrorMessage = case(
    ExecutionErrorMessage == '', "No Errors Found", ExecutionErrorMessage
)
| project ErrorMessage, DataEntityActivityRunID
| where DataEntityActivityRunID == ActivityRunID

let In_Progress =
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | project ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemRunStatus, Start_Time = ESTTime;
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | join kind=inner (In_Progress) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | extend Duration_Mins = datetime_diff('minute', ESTTime, Start_Time)
    | extend Last_Run_Duration = datetime_diff('minute', ESTTime - 1d, Start_Time - 1d)
    | project ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, ItemRunID, ItemRunStatus, EventDateTime = ESTTime, Duration_Mins, Last_Run_Duration
    | where EventDateTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York')) and ItemRunStatus in~ (PipelineRunStatus) 
    | order by EventDateTime desc

let Failed =    
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Failed"
    | project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, Failed_status = ItemRunStatus, Failed_time = EventDateTime;
let Succeeded =
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Succeeded"
    | project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, Success_status = ItemRunStatus, Success_time = EventDateTime;
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
    | join kind=leftouter (Succeeded) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | join kind=leftouter (Failed) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "In Progress" and Failed_status == '' and Success_status == '' and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | project  ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, PipelineRunID = ItemRunID, EventDateTime = ESTTime, ItemRunStatus
    | order by EventDateTime desc

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend Day = format_datetime(EventDateTime, 'yyyy-MM-dd')
    | project ItemRunStatus, EventDateTime, Day
	| where EventDateTime >= ago(7d)
    | summarize countItemRunStatus = count() by ItemRunStatus, Day
    | order  by Day asc

Item_Data_Entity_Refined
| extend Day = format_datetime(DataEntityStartDateTime, 'yyyy-MM-dd')
| project DataEntityStartDateTime, InsertCount, DataEntityName, Day
| where InsertCount != '' and DataEntityStartDateTime >= ago(7d)
| summarize Total_Insert_Count = sum(InsertCount) by Day, DataEntityName
| order by Day asc

Item_Data_Entity_Refined 
| extend Day = format_datetime(DataEntityStartDateTime, 'yyyy-MM-dd')
| project DataEntityStartDateTime, InsertCount, Day
| where InsertCount != '' and DataEntityStartDateTime >= ago(7d)
| summarize Total_Insert_Count = sum(InsertCount) by Day
| order by Day asc;

let Failed =    
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Failed"
    | project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, Failed_status = ItemRunStatus, Failed_time = EventDateTime;
let Succeeded =
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | where ItemRunStatus == "Succeeded"
    | project ItemID, ItemRunID, ItemWorkspaceName, Success_status = ItemRunStatus, Success_time = EventDateTime;
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
    | join kind=leftouter (Succeeded) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | join kind=leftouter (Failed) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ItemRunStatus == "In Progress" and Failed_status == '' and Success_status == '' and ParentItemID == '' and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | project  ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, PipelineRunID = ItemRunID, ItemRunStatus, EventDateTime = ESTTime
    | order by EventDateTime desc

let Child = 
    Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ParentItemID != '' and ItemRunStatus in~ (PipelineRunStatus) and EventDateTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | project ItemWorkspaceName, ItemID, Child_Pipeline = ItemName, ItemRunID, End_Status = ItemRunStatus, End_Time = ESTTime, ParentItemID, ParentItemName
    | order by End_Time desc;
let End =    
Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ParentItemID == '' and ItemRunStatus in~ (PipelineRunStatus) and EventDateTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | project ItemWorkspaceName, ItemID, PipelineName = ItemName, ItemRunID, End_Status = ItemRunStatus, End_Time = ESTTime
    | order by End_Time desc;
Item_Execution_InProgress_Refined
    | join kind=inner (End) on ItemID and ItemRunID
    | join kind=inner (Child) on $left.ItemName == $right.ParentItemName
    | extend ESTTime = EventDateTime - 4h
    | where ParentItemID == '' and ItemRunStatus == "In Progress" and ESTTime >= startofday(datetime_utc_to_local(now(), 'America/New_York'))
    | extend Duration_Mins = datetime_diff('minute', End_Time, ESTTime)
    | extend Last_Run_Duration = datetime_diff('minute', End_Time - 1d, ESTTime - 1d)
    | project ItemWorkspaceName, PipelineName = ItemName, PipelineRunID = ItemRunID, ItemRunStatus = End_Status, ChildPipelineName = Child_Pipeline, EventDateTime = End_Time, Duration_Mins, Last_Run_Duration 
    | order by EventDateTime desc

ItemDataEntity
| distinct ItemRunID

ItemDataEntity
| distinct DataEntityActivityRunID

Item_Execution_Completed_Refined
| distinct ItemRunStatus
